<sect1 id="Annotator.Scaling">
	<title>Scale Concepts/Relations by Type</title>
	<para>
		The Scale Concept/Relation by Type Annotator allows users to change the
		size of concepts or relations depending on their concept class or
		relation type.
	</para>
